{"tid":2035874,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"係公司最重要係坐返個好嘅位","createTime":"2020-05-26T06:52:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T14:37:23.000Z","uid":56874,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e455768ad98bc3833a1b7aa3bbbe0666c5da6e7e","tid":2035874,"uid":56874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T06:52:36.000Z","msg":"背面係牆就最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我依家個位背面係行人通度，每個鐘都有差唔多成10個同事經過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時諗諗下野，d同事行得快就會好似有陣風係個後腦到吹過，諗諗下野都斷左...好煩擾呀...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時比佢地行來行去攪到冇埋心機做野<br />\n新工離，初時冇咩野，但已經忍左幾個月啦，開始忍唔到...開始有d炆<br />\n想為左個位而辭職...會唔會好傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cdcd49adf1c476c56566bed6c5bdcd7b1fc8196","tid":2035874,"uid":294121,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T06:54:08.000Z","msg":"將你個位搬入廁所無人阻到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a214a20d3c7e505e566af66109458028aa58286","tid":2035874,"uid":122134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T06:55:27.000Z","msg":"風水都有講呢個因素<br />\n咁樣行黎行去<br />\n事業想專注都難"},{"pid":"25e66c031a85108f649ad9f056979930e43e6516","tid":2035874,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T06:55:46.000Z","msg":"我坐走廊近廁所位 成日按手機都比上司老細見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd7dc71e67c518a2ab1de508a9c1834d2e85d0fe","tid":2035874,"uid":301508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T06:58:34.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n坐埋一二邊<br />\n走左都冇人知嘅位最爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abfa82332b4fd4a989300784706ac4a70a2d05d5","tid":2035874,"uid":56874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9a214a20d3c7e505e566af66109458028aa58286","tid":2035874,"uid":122134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T06:55:27.000Z","msg":"風水都有講呢個因素<br />\n咁樣行黎行去<br />\n事業想專注都難"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T06:58:48.000Z","msg":"其實係咪嫁，堅想辭職，因為有時佢地係咁去影印，真係勁多人行離行去<br />\n一來立即唔想諗野，二來忍左一排之後依家係開始炆啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想為左個位辭職...會唔會好傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我直屬上司又幾好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4258855488bbf6b2b359ffdf411983762168989d","tid":2035874,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T07:00:11.000Z","msg":"如果係認真做野<br />\n怕咩人行過<br />\n想人行過望到添喇"},{"pid":"ba19793901bb4fd03b8128c7f7f35af08b5bb7e8","tid":2035874,"uid":56874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25e66c031a85108f649ad9f056979930e43e6516","tid":2035874,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T06:55:46.000Z","msg":"我坐走廊近廁所位 成日按手機都比上司老細見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T07:00:11.000Z","msg":"我唔係怕按手機比人睇到呀<br />\n我真係想做野，但成日好似有陣風係後腦到<br />\n諗諗下野斷左同埋開始好炆啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd6a4e70e54fc1ffa9c57b4ab75232444daf020e","tid":2035874,"uid":56874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4258855488bbf6b2b359ffdf411983762168989d","tid":2035874,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T07:00:11.000Z","msg":"如果係認真做野<br />\n怕咩人行過<br />\n想人行過望到添喇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T07:02:05.000Z","msg":"我真想做野，我唔怕比人望個mon呀<br />\n但你明唔明，但多人行過，同埋佢地行得急嘅時間會好似有陣風吹過個後腦咁，好騷擾到我諗野做野呀<br />\n條走廊又窄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c092cc706194a981720c3a992f22551cac62b22","tid":2035874,"uid":52459,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2